---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
---
<Layout
  title="Retaining Walls Beaconsfield VIC | Sleeper, Block & Concrete | Free Quote"
  description="Specialist retaining wall builders for Beaconsfield and Beaconsfield Upper. Steep blocks need engineered walls — we deliver. Free fixed-price quotes — call (03) 9003 0223."
  canonical="https://pakenhamretainingwalls.com.au/beaconsfield/">

  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-inner">
      <span class="hero-eyebrow">Beaconsfield VIC 3807</span>
      <h1>Retaining walls for <span class="accent">Beaconsfield</span> &amp; Beaconsfield Upper.</h1>
      <p class="hero-sub">
        Beaconsfield Upper is the steepest block country in the south-east. Acreage,
        granite outcrops, and long sloping driveways. We build the engineered walls
        these blocks demand &mdash; not the temporary fixes that fail in five years.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030223">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0223</a>
        <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Get a free quote</a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <span class="section-eyebrow">Beaconsfield specifics</span>
      <h2>Acreage retaining walls done right.</h2>
      <div class="divider"></div>

      <div style="max-width: 60rem;">
        <p>
          Beaconsfield Upper sits in the foothills of the Dandenong Ranges. The blocks here
          are large &mdash; often 1&ndash;5 acres &mdash; with steep falls, granite, scattered gum
          trees, and septic systems instead of mains sewer. The retaining walls we build
          here are bigger, longer, and more engineered than anywhere else in the Cardinia.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Typical Beaconsfield Upper wall jobs</h3>
        <ul>
          <li><strong>Driveway retaining (long runs)</strong> &mdash; 30&ndash;80m of wall along a sloping driveway, typically 1.2&ndash;2m high. Concrete sleeper or block.</li>
          <li><strong>House pad walls</strong> &mdash; large engineered walls supporting a cut-in house platform on a sloped block.</li>
          <li><strong>Tiered terraces</strong> &mdash; rather than one massive wall, multiple stepped walls of 600mm&ndash;900mm with planted terraces between.</li>
          <li><strong>Stable / shed cuts</strong> &mdash; flat platforms for sheds, garages, stables, and pool houses cut into the slope.</li>
        </ul>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Engineering on every Beaconsfield Upper job over 1m</h3>
        <p>
          Walls over 1m on acreage almost always need engineering certification &mdash; especially
          where they support structures above (house, shed, driveway) or where neighbouring
          land is involved. We arrange the engineer, the soil test, and the council lodgement
          as part of the package. No "near enough is good enough" walls.
        </p>

        <h3 style="margin-top: 2rem;">Beaconsfield (lower) and Officer South</h3>
        <p>
          The lower Beaconsfield streets and Officer South have flatter blocks and standard
          residential retaining wall jobs &mdash; rear yards, pool surrounds, garden beds.
          We do those too, with the same engineering and drainage standards.
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section section-alt">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <h2>Wall types we build in Beaconsfield.</h2>
      <div class="svc-grid">
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/timber-retaining-walls/"><h3>Timber sleeper</h3><p>Most economical, 15&ndash;40 year lifespan.</p><span class="svc-link">Details &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/concrete-sleeper-walls/"><h3>Concrete sleeper</h3><p>50+ year lifespan, ideal for taller walls.</p><span class="svc-link">Details &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/block-retaining-walls/"><h3>Block / masonry</h3><p>Premium look, long lifespan.</p><span class="svc-link">Details &rarr;</span></a>
        <a class="svc-card" href="/services/excavation-earthworks/"><h3>Earthworks</h3><p>Cut-and-fill, drainage, levelling.</p><span class="svc-link">Details &rarr;</span></a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="section">
    <div class="section-inner">
      <div class="cta-block">
        <h2>Beaconsfield site visit &mdash; free.</h2>
        <p>Book a free measure-up and fixed-price quote.</p>
        <div class="hero-actions" style="justify-content:center;">
          <a class="btn btn-primary" href="tel:+61390030223">&#9742; Call (03) 9003 0223</a>
          <a class="btn btn-ghost" href="/quote/">Quote online</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
